[0.000088, "o", "╭────┬────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n│    │ Control name                   │ Docs                                      │\r\n├────┼────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n│ ❌ │ Allow privilege escalation     │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0016 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Host PID/IPC privileges        │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0038 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Immutable container filesystem │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0017 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Insecure capabilities          │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0046 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Linux hardening                │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0055 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Non-root containers            │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0013 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Privileged container           │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0057 │\r\n╰────┴────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────╯\r\n"]
