[0.000123, "o", "╭────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n│    │ Control name                                          │ Docs                                      │\r\n├────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n│ ✅ │ CVE-2021-25741 - Using symlink for arbitrary host ... │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0058 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Configured liveness probe                             │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0056 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Configured readiness probe                            │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0018 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Deprecated serviceAccount field                       │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0294 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Duplicate environment variable                        │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0295 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Exposed sensitive interfaces                          │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0021 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Image pull policy on latest tag                       │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0075 │\r\n│ ✅ │ K8s common labels usage                               │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0077 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Label usage for resources                             │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0076 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Mount service principal                               │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0020 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Naked pods                                            │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0073 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Pods in default namespace                             │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0061 │\r\n│ ✅ │ SSH server running inside container                   │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0042 │\r\n│ ❌ │ Service with no workload                              │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0293 │\r\n│ ✅ │ Sudo in container entrypoint                          │ https://kubescape.io/docs/controls/c-0062 │\r\n╰────┴────────────