[0.126134, "o", "Name:         ci-egress-restriction\r\nNamespace:    ci\r\nCreated on:   2026-07-01 20:37:24 +0200 CEST\r\nLabels:       <none>\r\nAnnotations:  description:\r\n                Restricts egress traffic from deep dive challenge pipelines. Allows only the traffic needed by the build pipeline: DNS, K8s API, Gitea, lo...\r\nSpec:\r\n  PodSelector:     <none> (Allowing the specific traffic to all pods in this namespace)\r\n  Not affecting ingress traffic\r\n  Allowing egress traffic:\r\n    To Port: 53/UDP\r\n    To Port: 53/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=kube-system\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 443/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: <none>\r\n      PodSelector: component=apiserver\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 3000/TCP\r\n    To Port: 22/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=gitea\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 5000/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=registry\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 8443/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=tekton-pipelines\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 8081/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=kourier-system\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 8080/TCP\r\n    To:\r\n      NamespaceSelector: kubernetes.io/metadata.name=release-pipeline\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: 443/TCP\r\n    To: <any> (traffic not restricted by destination)\r\n    ----------\r\n    To Port: <any> (traffic allowed to all ports)\r\n    To:\r\n      PodSelector: <none>\r\n  Policy Types: Egress\r\n"]
