[0.000022, "o", "\u001b[0mYou are in 'detached HEAD' state. You can look around, make experimental\r\n\u001b[92m\u001b[92;1m[clone-pr-code : clone] \u001b[0mchanges and commit them, and you can discard any commits you make in this\r\n\u001b[92m\u001b[92;1m[clone-pr-code : clone] "]
